                About Our Ranch	
            </div>
            <p>In the Year 1992, Captain Brook bought a creek-fed oasis in the Chalbi Desert of Nothern Kenya, sparking generations of integrity, preservation, and innovation called Brook Ranch.
The Ranch now covers 825,000 acres in the County of Machakos. 
 </p>
  
