            <h2>Testimonial</h2>
            <blockquote>
            <p>The Ranch – surrounded by the scenic beauty of farms and ranches in the rolling hills of Nunnelly, TN – provides a full spectrum of addiction treatment services. The Ranch’s experientially based program is designed to meet the needs of each individual and provide techniques to explore the feelings and behaviors that hold them hostage. The Ranch moves individuals from “survive” to “thrive” by supporting each client and family member in an effort to help them meet their authentic self. Co-occurring disorders, destructive character patterns, skills deficits and life management issues seriously compromise the sobriety, safety and health of each individual. The Ranch addresses these underlying issues and promote a sense of belonging, connection and self-actualization.
            </p>
            
            <cite><a href="#">Robert Millikin</a> - <span>Marketing Director<BR><a href="#"> More reviews...<br></a></span></cite>
